    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied across all five operating points. Assessment team accepts the simulation evidence as adequate to support the regulatory submission decision. Compliance with project requirements is documented in the design history file.",
